TopicTitle: Classic Airliner mods? (Other than Airplanes plus and KAX)

Articles.Content:
Looking for like JT8D, 737-200, 707, etc style planes.
I saw KK was working on one, but idk where he went.
NeistAir has a whole bunch of airliner cockpits, which are all pretty good. SXT continued has a bunch of plane parts alongside its stockalike rocket bits, too.
